# Environment Configuration for GitHub Repository Summarizer
# 
# INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Edit .env and replace the placeholder with your actual API key
# 3. Choose ONE provider and uncomment its line
#
# The .env file is git-ignored for security

# For Nebius Token Factory (recommended - free credits available)
# Sign up at: https://studio.nebius.ai/
NEBIUS_API_KEY=your-nebius-api-key-here

# Alternative providers (uncomment ONE and add your key):
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-anthropic-api-key-here
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key-here
